Class StandardResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • chav1961.funnypro.core.StandardResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FProPluginList, IResolvable

    public class StandardResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements IResolvable, FProPluginList

    This class is a standard resolver for all built-in predicates and operators, described in I.Bratko. Use this class as an example for development your own plugins

    Since:
    0.0.1
    Author:
    Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
